column2: Cloudless sky- lots of aquatic plants in water.
No rain past week- clear day- slight wind.  Weedy.
Clear- slight wind. rainstorm 3 days ago- sediment in water.
Cloudy- slgiht wind. choppy water- no recent rain.
Clear- cold. slightly choppy water.  No recent rain.
Clear- breezy- some waves.  Snow 5 days ago.
Semi-cloudy.  No boat traffic.  No rain- still water.
Sunny- cool. Fair amount of boat traffic.
Partly cloudy- some wind and low waves.
Sunny- no clouds- clear water. Normal boat traffic.
Sunny- pollen on surface water near shore. Slight breeze. No boat traffic.
Partially cloudy. Little boat traffic- choppy water with wind.
Hazy- clouds. Calm water. No boat traffic.
Mostly cloudy with little sunlight. Slight breeze with small waves.
Some wind with choppy water. Partly cloudy.
Partly cloudy- some wind and small waves. More boat traffic than last week.
Sunny- no wind. Little boat traffic. Clear water.
Partly cloudy (1st time able to test in 5 days). Slight wind and waves. Little boat traffic. 2.5" rain in past few days.
Mostly sunny- quite windy- so exact reading  is difficult at best b/c of lack of perpendicular reading.
Clear day. Very windy and rain yesterday. Some wind and slight waves today.
Breezy- making observation more difficult. More sediment in water.
Breezy- semi-clear day.  Observations difficult. Less sediment. Hard to find clear day.
Some wind and slight choppiness. No boat traffic.
Partly cloudy. Cool.  Slight breeze- no boat traffic.
Partly cloudy- some wind and some choppiness of water.
Clear day- slight wind and slight waves. No boat traffic.
Clear day- no waves.  Best day yet for readings. No boat traffic.
Clear day after days of rain.  No wind- no traffic.
Partly cloudy- no boat traffic- slight breeze.
clear day- quiet lake.  No traffic
Partly cloudy- slight breeze- lake quiet
Partly cloudy- slight breeze.  Some traffic.
Slight breeze- no boat traffic. Water very low.  Partly cloudy
Nice day (after 2 weeks of lousy- rainy windy days)
clear day- finally! slight breeze- no boat traffic- ice out 10 days ago
clear day (rare) slight wind- not much boat traffic yet
clear day- no boat traffic- a lot of pollen on H2O
mostly clear- slight breeze- no boat traffic
mostly clear- slight breeze- very little boat traffic
partly cloudy- slight breeze- little traffic
Partly cloudy- slight breeze.  Very little boat traffic.
Clear day- little traffic- slight wind.
Partly cloudy- slight breeze.  No boat traffic.  Many more weeds than 2 weeks ago.
Colder spell.  Windy past few days.  Partly cloudy.
Colder (50s)- calm and clear.  Lake down - level very low.
Colder.  2 inches of rain last 48 hours.  Slight breeze- no boat traffic.
a lot windy- temp guage non-operational- phosphorus checked
partly cloudy- slight wind- no boats
Some breeze.  Cloudy water.  More weeds.
Sunny and clear. In the 80's beautiful
Cloudy- still- after a rain 12 hrs- water temp 58
Calm- 2 fishing boats- 1 bald eagle- smoky sky from Canadian wildfire
One fishing boat on the lake.  Lots of fish sightings.
